body.prompt:
Generate a fake conversation between a customer and an agent.
The agent should introduce themselves, their company and give the customer
their name. The agent should ask for the customer's name.
As part of the conversation, have the agent ask for two pieces of
personal information.  Spell out numbers. For example, 1000 should be
said as one zero zero zero, not one thousand. The conversation should be
at least 10 lines long and be complete. At the end
of the conversation, the agent should thank the customer for their time
and end the conversation. Return the conversation formatted 
like the following example:

{'conversation': 
    [
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': 'xxxxx'}, 
    {'speaker': 'Customer', 'message': "xxxxx."}, 
    {'speaker': 'Agent', 'message': "xxxxxx"}
    ] 
}

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Hello, my name is George Stewart and I'm with Auto Elite Car Dealership. May I have your name, please?

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Nice to meet you, Elizabeth. How can I assist you today? I understand you have a concern about product quality. Is that correct?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Yes, that's right. I recently purchased a car from your dealership and I've been experiencing some issues.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I'm sorry to hear that. Could you provide me with the VIN number of your vehicle, which is a unique seventeen-digit code?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: Sure, the VIN number is one two three four five six seven eight nine zero one two.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: Thank you, Elizabeth. May I also have your current mileage reading on the vehicle?

body.speaker: Customer
body.message: My current mileage is seven zero zero zero zero miles.

body.speaker: Agent
body.message: I appreciate the information, Elizabeth. We will review your concerns and reach out to you with a resolution soon. Thank you for your time.
